<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="/business/internet/nodemobile_data/">Static IP services are available for an extra $5 per month</a></strong></p>
<h3>Coverage and Performance</h3>
<p>NodeMobile Data is an Internode broadband service delivered via the Optus mobile networks, which now cover over 97% of Australia's population*.</p>
<ul>
<li>* Some coverage limitations apply, please refer to our <a href="https://secure.internode.on.net/webtools/nodemobile-coverage-checker">Online Coverage Checker</a>.</li>
<li>The speed that you obtain will vary depending on a number of factors, which are presented on our <a href="/residential/wireless_broadband/nodemobile_data/performance/">NodeMobile Data Performance</a> page.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your choice of contract and hardware</h3>
<p>Choose either a one month contract, or a 24 month contract with reduced hardware prices:</p>
<ul>
<li>Choose a Huawei E3131 3G USB modem - it's no additional change on a 24 month contract.</li>
<li>Alternatively, enjoy the freedom and flexibility of <a href="/residential/wireless_broadband/nodemobile_data/hardware/portable_hotspot/">your own portable 3G/WiFi hotspot</a> - now just $29 on a 24 month contract.</li>
</ul>
<p>Or if you already have your own compatible hardware, simply choose a SIM. We offer the full range of regular SIMs; MicroSIMs (iPad-compatible); and now NanoSIMs for the iPad mini.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/residential/wireless_broadband/nodemobile_data/hardware/"><strong>Check out the hardware options</strong></a></li>
</ul>
<h3>Avoid '3G bill shock'</h3>
<p>Keep your mobile broadband costs completely under your control. Simply choose from our wide range of options the monthly plan that suits your mobile broadband needs.</p>
<p>There's no automatic 'excess usage charges' on NodeMobile. Instead, you can buy a Data Block anytime if you need more than your monthly quota - and you can change plans even if you're under contract.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/residential/product_features/data_blocks/nodemobile_data/"><strong>All about NodeMobile Data Blocks</strong></a></li>
</ul>
<h3>More than just the Internet</h3>
<p>You'll find NodeMobile Data delivers much more than just wireless broadband. We've packed it with useful features and a range of convenient options.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/residential/wireless_broadband/nodemobile_data/features/"><strong>Learn more about NodeMobile Data Features</strong></a></li>
</ul>
<h3>Questions?</h3>
<p>If you&rsquo;ve got questions, chances are we have the answers in our <a href="/residential/wireless_broadband/nodemobile_data/faq/">NodeMobile Data FAQs</a>.</p>
<ul>
<li>And if you need any help, please <a href="/contact/sales/">contact us</a>.</li>
</ul>	
